  <brief_title>Normal and Abnormal ERP During ToM and Emotional Conflicts in Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <acronym>SERC</acronym>
  <official_title>Normal and Abnormal Event Related Potentials During Attribution of Intentions to Others and Resolution of Emotional Conflicts in Schizophrenia</official_title>
